HEADWORD: Prompt-note
<hw>Prompt"-note`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Com.)</fld>
<def>A memorandum of a sale, and time when payment is due, given to the
purchaser at a sale of goods.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

